{"version":1,"entries":{"person_2937438_translations":{"at":1772469922630,"data":{"id":2937438,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"赵晴，2000年8月4日出生于黑龙江省 ，毕业于浙江传媒学院，中国内地影视女演员 。\n\n赵晴原本是拍摄汉服的网红 。2021年，赵晴开始尝试演戏，主演古装爱情剧《一纸寄风月》，从而进入演艺圈 ；同年，主演的奇幻轻喜剧《贩卖法术的杂货铺》播出 。2022年7月，出演奇幻爱情轻喜剧《差一分的谎言》 ；8月，主演的都市爱情短剧《别惹前女友》播出 。2023年5月，赵晴与李小冉等合作出演的非遗题材网剧《正好遇见你》播出，并在剧中饰演珍妃； 10月，与周也、王星越领衔主演的古装女性成长疗愈剧《为有暗香来》播出，饰演仲夜阑的心上人牧遥 ，而该剧的视频累计播放量为1386.5万 。2024年3月30日，参加的青年演员演技研习真人秀《无限超越班第二季》播出 ；6月2日，参演的古装爱情剧《墨雨云间》播出 ；9月22日，参加2024秋季搜狐视频播主大会 ；同年，入选文荣奖青年演员扶持计划名单 ；10月24日，领衔主演的古装剧《探晴安》播出 。11月，入选2024星辰大海青年演员名单。 2025年1月25日，参演的古装爱情喜剧《五福临门》播出 ；2月13日，主演的电视剧《怎敌她千娇百媚》播出 。","name":"赵晴","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Чжао Цин","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"趙晴，中國大陸女演員。出生於黑龍江，畢業於浙江傳媒學院。2021年以主演古裝愛情劇《一紙寄風月》的正式踏入演藝圈。","name":"趙晴","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"Triệu Tình (赵晴), sinh năm 2000, tốt nghiệp Học viện Truyền thông Chiết Giang. Nữ diễn viên trẻ chỉ mới bắt đầu sự nghiệp diễn xuất từ năm 2021, từng tham gia một số bộ phim chiếu mạng như Vy Vũ Yến Song Phi, Manh Chủ Đại Lý Tự, Áo Mới Của Công Chúa... Cô nàng thường được ví von có khí chất và nhan sắc giống với mỹ nữ Chúc Tự Đan","name":"Triệu Tình","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Zhao Qing, an internet celebrity in the Hanfu circle, was born in Hangzhou, Zhejiang, and graduated from Zhejiang Media College.\n\nIn 2021, Zhao Qing makes her acting debut as the second female lead in the web drama: 'Palace: Devious Women', produced by the famous screenwriter, Yu Zheng of Huanyu Entertainment","name":"Zhao Qing","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"조청","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"趙晴，中國大陸女演員。出生於黑龍江，畢業於浙江傳媒學院。2021 年以主演古裝愛情劇《一紙寄風月》的正式踏入演藝圈。","name":"趙晴","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Чжао Цін","primary":false}}]}},"person_5958665_translations":{"at":1772469926045,"data":{"id":5958665,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Nikki Macaluso","primary":true}}]}},"person_2123084_translations":{"at":1772469928079,"data":{"id":2123084,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Jin Ye-sol","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"진예솔","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"陈艺瑟","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"陳藝瑟","primary":false}}]}},"person_2745297_translations":{"at":1772469935166,"data":{"id":2745297,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Male singer from mainland China and a member of the boy group SWIN . He graduated from the Sichuan Conservatory of Music. In 2014, Zuo Qibo signed a contract with Faith Music Records; in January of the same year, he directed the short film \" Stealing My Two Years of Time","name":"Zuo Qibo","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"Zuo Qibo","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Цзо Ци Бо","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"左其铂","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"左其鉑","primary":false}}]}},"person_1185786_translations":{"at":1772469938187,"data":{"id":1185786,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Liu ShiShi (Cecilia Liu) graduated from Beijing Dance Academy, major in Ballet. During her college time, she once had a opportunity to play a role in a TV series. It was that chance that open a new path for the ballerina's future. Upon her graduation from the Academy, she decided to choose acting as her career.\n\nShiShi is best known for her role as RuoXi in Chinese period drama Scarlet Heart, 2011. Due to the great success of this TV series and her great performance during and after Scarlet Heart, she was named as one of the \"Chinese Four Promising Young Famale actresses\" by the famous Chinese paper-media Nan Du Entertainment Weekly in 2013.\n\nLiu ShiShi has been married to Taiwanese actor Nicky Wu on Jan 20th 2015, whom she met on the set of Scarlet Heart in 2011.\n\nNow ShiShi is focusing on big screen, preferring roles that realistic complex, challenging and nurturing.","name":"Liu Shishi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"류시시","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"刘诗诗（1987年3月10日－），本名刘诗施，回族，中国大陆知名女演员，毕业于北京舞蹈学院芭蕾舞系02级本科班。2004年因出演电视剧《月影风荷》步入演艺圈。2007年正式签约经纪公司，先后出演《射雕英雄传》、《仙剑奇侠传三》、《天涯织女》、《怪侠一枝梅》等多部电视剧。2011年因主演《步步惊心》走红。之后她开始进军大银幕，拍摄了《不二神探》、《回到爱开始的地方》、《绣春刀》、《深夜前的五分钟》、《心理罪之城市之光》等电影作品。","name":"刘诗诗","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"SK","iso_639_1":"sk","name":"Slovenčina","english_name":"Slovak","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"Lưu Thi Thi là một nữ diễn viên người Trung Quốc. Cô tốt nghiệp khoa múa ba lê của Học viện múa Bắc Kinh, nhưng sau đó cô chuyển hướng trở thành diễn viên và thành công với vai diễn Mã Nhĩ Thái Nhược Hy trong Bộ bộ kinh tâm, bộ phim truyền hình mà cô đóng cặp với Ngô Kỳ Long.","name":"Lưu Thi Thi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"劉詩詩","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Лю Ши Ши","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"劉詩詩（1987 年 3 月 10 日－），本名劉詩施，回族，中國大陸知名女演員，畢業於北京舞蹈學院芭蕾舞系 02 級本科班。2004 年因出演電視劇《月影風荷》步入演藝圈。2007 年正式簽約經紀公司，先後出演《射鵰英雄傳》、《仙劍奇俠傳三》、《天涯織女》、《怪俠一枝梅》等多部電視劇。2011 年因主演《步步驚心》走紅。之後她開始進軍大銀幕，拍攝了《不二神探》、《回到愛開始的地方》、《繡春刀》、《深夜前的五分鐘》、《心理罪之城市之光》等電影作品。","name":"劉詩詩","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"หลิวซือซือ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}}]}},"person_2202330_translations":{"at":1772469938988,"data":{"id":2202330,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Erol Yavan","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TR","iso_639_1":"tr","name":"Türkçe","english_name":"Turkish","data":{"biography":"","name":"Erol Yavan","primary":true}}]}},"movie_1146344_credits":{"at":1772469939007,"data":{"id":1146344,"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":18182,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Olga Kurylenko","original_name":"Ольга Куриленко","popularity":4.0497,"profile_path":"/ei6eYUhQFw2AaV6U5fyPptBaPF0.jpg","cast_id":1,"